'''BRP''' can mean:* Basic Role-Playing game system* Blue Ridge Parkway* Bombardier Recreational Products, Canadian company* Brief reactive psychosis* British Racing Partnership, former British motor racing team* Bathroom privileges* ''Barko/Bapor ng Republika ng Pilipinas'' (ship/steamship of the Republic of the Philippines), Philippine Navy ship name prefix* "B.R.P.", song by Victor Jara on album ''El derecho de vivir en paz''* Brioche-purl stitch, in brioche knitting